des:
We are the most listened radio in Fetești and Cernavodă (survey 2022) and we are the radio audience leader in the 35+ age category.
We are listened to daily by over 18,000 unique listeners on air and around 2,000 listeners on the interneteverywhere in the world (website, applications, etc.).
We understand that good music will always have an audience and that the listener evolves. We understand our community role and that we needed to adapt, evolve and merge the power of radio with social media and the digital world to best serve the local community.
Leader in the office and in the car.
